# Ollama has no secrets today.
#
# This file exists so the per-app dir layout matches every other app and so
# the dotenv lookup in the reconciler doesn't error if anyone references ${VAR}
# from compose.yml later. To activate:
#
# 1. Copy to `.env` next to compose.yml.
# 2. Encrypt with:  ansible-vault encrypt servers/truenas/apps/ollama/.env
#
# If/when an Ollama API token is introduced (OLLAMA_API_KEY etc.), add it here
# and reference it from compose.yml as ${OLLAMA_API_KEY}.
